### 核销券退款接口测试
### 基础配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. 申请退款 - 正常流程
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/apply
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{token}}

{
  "voucher_id": 1,
  "refund_reason": "不想要了"
}

### 2. 申请退款 - 券不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/apply
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{token}}

{
  "voucher_id": 99999,
  "refund_reason": "测试"
}

### 3. 申请退款 - 已使用的券(应失败)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/apply
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{token}}

{
  "voucher_id": 2,
  "refund_reason": "已经使用了"
}

### 4. 申请退款 - 重复申请(应失败)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/apply
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{token}}

{
  "voucher_id": 1,
  "refund_reason": "再次申请"
}

### 5. 退款详情 - 正常查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/detail?id=1
token: {{token}}

### 6. 退款详情 - 退款记录不存在
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/detail?id=99999
token: {{token}}

### 7. 退款列表 - 全部
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/lists
token: {{token}}

### 8. 退款列表 - 申请中
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/lists?state=0
token: {{token}}

### 9. 退款列表 - 同意退款
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/lists?state=1
token: {{token}}

### 10. 退款列表 - 拒绝退款
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/lists?state=2
token: {{token}}

### 11. 退款列表 - 退款成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/refund/lists?state=3
token: {{token}}
